# Prefer Simple Tools (SHOULD)

grug like tools that do one thing well

When choosing tool:
- Is it simple to understand?
- Does it solve real problem?
- Will team be able to maintain it?
- Is documentation clear?

Fancy new tool often more trouble than worth
